We do not knowingly contact or collect personal information from children under 16. If you become aware that your child has provided us with personal information without your consent, please contact us. If we become aware that a child under 16 has provided us with personal information, we take steps to remove such information and terminate the child’s account.
No ad companies collect data through our service
:
We do not allow advertising companies to collect data through our service for ad targeting.
